flowRoot.flowPara: There once was a thing called online privacy.
It kept all your secret information safe.
Then one day an alien named Zucc appeared and made a platform for everyone's secrets
He grew his platform worldwide and got hold of many secrets
Zucc realized he could use these secrets to make money
Eventually others saw they too could make money with secrets
Zucc collected and collected people's secrets
Until one day he made a mistake.
Zucc gave away personal secrets of 50 million people.
How The Zucc Stole Online Privacy
